lias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7744,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/near-far-neighbors\/","url_meta":{"origin":6016,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Neighbors: Charity to near neighbors before far neighbors","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I have two neighbors; to whom should I send my gifts?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTo the neighbor who is closest to your door.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5674 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/09\/07\/mercy-and-peace\/","url_meta":{"origin":6016,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Worship the Merciful, feed the poor, spread peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 7, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWorship the Most Merciful, feed the poor, and spread peace. You will enter Paradise in peace.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304\u00a01855 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064d\u0648 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u